description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride!  The crew needs to be a bit more age aware.  The Chief Love Officer might have a conflict of interest with these letters today.  The ladies have a way to get your man to crack.  Where in your house is the best place for space and ME time?  There is definitely one place you can go with yo raise and new attitude!  Sometimes the only thing in between our lives and death is our mouthpiece.  Junior is back with Truth Be Told and it has to deal with phone calls on a specific day at a specific time.  Ever gotten snipped?  Well we have a safer alternative.  Today in Closing Remarks, Steve warns us about what happens as we elevate ourselves.
